caption.text:
A WORKOUT?! Whaaaaat? Who is she?! Anyways, this was an absolutely KILLER & BOMB power body day! Filmed most of the exercises but for what I didn’t film, it’s listed down below 🖤⚡️
⠀⠀
🍓 warm up with dynamic hip openers, stationary lunges, body weight squats & Glute bridges
🍓 seated leg extensions 4 x 8-12 reps (not shown)
🍓 barbell back pause squats 3 x 8-10 reps
🍓 regular barbell back squats 3 x 10-12 reps
🍓 barbell RDLs 4 x 6-10 reps
🍓 reverse lunges 3 x 6-8 each leg
🍓 single leg elevated toe good mornings 3 x 10-12 each leg
🍓 overhead plate squats with elevated heels 2 x 10
🍓 lying leg curls 3 x 10-12
